      <h2>Summer (March – June)</h2>
      <p>240 GSM cotton breathes well despite its weight. In summer, pair an oversized graphic tee with jogger shorts and white sneakers. Stick to lighter colours — pista, beige, white — to reflect heat. Opt for loose fits to allow airflow.</p>
